&quot;Romelu Lukaku's ankle injury has also fully recovered. &quot;

Nacer Chadli came out of the game against Brazil by limping. He was present at the training session this Sunday in Moscow.<br />
<br />
&quot;I recovered well yesterday, I did not feel too good, but I feel much better today. It's important to recover well to be ready in two days. &quot;

&quot;It was silence in the locker room. The way we fought and the work done were huge. We can still play two more tournaments  (Euro 2020 and World Cup 2022) with this generation&quot;, Jan Vertonghen said.<br />
<br />
Vincent Kompany: &quot;Will I continue the adventure with the Red Devils? I do not know yet. All I can say at the moment is that I feel good.&quot;

